# Installation
1. In Streamer.bot in select `Import` from the top left.
Copy the `Import Code` and paste it into the `Import String`.
2. Add the Following References to the Code in the `Check Url` Action if needed.
```
mscorlib.dll
System.Text.RegularExpressions.dll
System.dll
```
3. You will need to set the `Check Url` Action to the `Chat Message Event`. 
4. Create a `Mod Only` Command tied to the `Permit User Url`. `!permit`
5. If you don't want Mods/VIPs to have the ability to post link change the `True` to `False`. (`Check URL` Action)
6. In `Permit User Url` Set the length you want the permit to be active for by changing the argument.
